title: BMW 7 series
description: The BMW 7 Series is a full-size luxury sedan manufactured and marketed by the German automaker BMW since 1977.

title: Lamborghini Sian
description: The Sián FKP 37 is the first super sports car powered by a V12 engine and hybrid technology based on supercapacitors.

title: Ford GT
description: The teardrop shape of the Ford GT is the result of extensive work in the wind tunnel. It has a carbon-fiber body and a 660-horsepower 3.5L EcoBoost® V6 engine.

title: Bentley Bentayga
description: Bentayga V8 and Bentayga S deliver a truly thrilling drive, reaching 0 to 60 mph in just 4.4 seconds (0 to 100 km/h in 4.5 seconds).

title: Mercedes Benz G63
description: All G63s come with a twin-turbocharged 4.0-liter V-8 engine that makes 577 horsepower and 627 lb-ft of torque.
